high_descs: Turn to your left then walk straight turn right facing the sink
Pick up the knife in the in front of the sink
Turn to your right then head to he island beside the stove
Slice the tomato on the top of the island
Put the knife on top of the island
Pick up the slice tomato on the island
Turn to your left then walk straight, turn right to the microwave
Open the microwave heat the tomato then get it back close the microwave
Turn to your right then cross the room head to the trash bin
Drop the slice tomato on the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice tomato in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight and turn to the right to go to the sink
pick up the knife near the sink.
Turn around, walk slightly a head, make a left turn to go to the counter top near the golden trash can.
Cut the tomato on the counter top
Put the knife on top of the fork and nest to the lettuce on the counter top.
Pick up the slice of tomato.
Turn around and walk to the right to go back to the sink.
Open the microwave on top of the sink, heat the tomato for a few seconds, pick it up again and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the left to the trash can.
Put the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato in the golden trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to face the sink on the right.
Grab the knife from in front of the sink.
Turn around and head left to the counter next to the trash can.
Slice up the tomato.
Place the knife next to the lettuce.
Grab a tomato slice.
Turn around and walk and face the microwave above the sink on the right.
Heat the tomato slice for 2 seconds.
Turn left and walk to the trash can.
Put the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed tomato slice in the trash can.
